  <scopecontent id="aspace_65d70a637c927ca7167c17e1c56edfa6">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Files of Constance E. Cook as Cornell's Vice President for Land Grant Affairs include records of special events; budgets, salaries, audits, and other financial records; personnel; buildings; State University of New York; statutory colleges at Cornell; and reports, correspondence, and related records.</p>  </scopecontent>
